elements.name: TS_RegisteredCheckout_02 - Registered User of 6thstreet.com site should be able to place order using cod

steps.name: User clicks on login link
User enters valid login details "validuser" username and "validuser" password in the login popup
User clicks on login button
user login is successfull
Home page is displayed
User clears cart
user enters product name as "LCW-8S7179Z4-LCW-TURQUOIS" in search text box and click search icon
user clicks on product tile in result
user selects countrySize as "EU", size as "10Y"
user clicks on ADDTOBAG button
user navigates to shopping bag page and clicks on proceedToCheckout button
user enters the valid details for shipping address
user selects payment option as "COD"
user clicks on place order button
Order placing should be successful

steps.name: Launch Admin Magento URL "MagentoURL"
User enters magento valid login details "magentouser" username and "magentouser" password in the login popup
User clicks on magento login button
user should be landed into Magento dashboard
user clicks on sales module
user clicks on order sub module
user should be landed into Orders page
user clicks on Filters button
user enters the order ID
user clicks on Apply Filters button
Search result should be displayed
user clicks on view link
user is in order details page
Verify Magento Order Status to be "Processing"

comments.value: #And Verify the Payment Method in Magento as "Pay in installments"

Verify Magento Order Status to be "Payment Aborted"
